text: Fernando De la Cruz (born January 25, 1971) is a former baseball player in Japan. de la Cruz played for the Osaka Kintetsu Buffaloes in the Japan Pacific League. ==References== ==External links== *https://www.baseball- reference.com/register/player.fcgi?id=desgue002fer Category:Dominican Republic expatriate baseball players in Japan Category:Osaka Kintetsu Buffaloes players Category:Living people Category:1971 births
title: Fernando de la Cruz
